                    <span>I bought this book because I was really craving a book written by an iranian so I could relate to... The book is well written if you want to have some fun laughing at extremely superficial issues about iranians living in the US, but totally lacks a real understanding of the situation. In few words this was a teenager book although I would not even recommend it to teenagers to read</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Too shallow, even for summer reading</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
